
# 🔹 FULL DETAILED UI PROMPT — READLY PLATFORM (ENHANCED)

> **Role:** You are a senior product designer and UX architect specialized in EdTech platforms for children.
> **Goal:** Design the complete UI/UX of a web-based educational platform called **Readly**, focused on story-based riddles for children.
> **Target users:** Children (primary users), Parents/Educators, and Admins.
> **Tone:** Friendly, playful, safe, educational, and non-overstimulating.
> **Platform:** Web application (desktop + tablet + mobile responsive).
> **Design system:** Modern, clean, child-friendly UI using rounded components, soft shadows, pastel colors, and accessible typography.

