## 7. HINT SYSTEM UI (AI-POWERED)

### Hint Button
* **Default:** Disabled; gray; no pointer.
* **After wrong attempt:** Enabled; label “Get a hint” or lightbulb icon; soft glow (e.g. `box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(245,184,76,0.4)`); 48px height.

### Hint Modal / Slide Panel
* **Title:** “Let’s think together” — 20px; friendly tone.
* **Level indicator:** “Hint 1 of 3” or dots (1–2–3); 14px; current level emphasized.
* **Content:** Hint text 18px; optional image (max 200px height); optional audio play button.
* **Actions:** “Got it” / “Next hint” (if more available); “Close”; no “Show answer” in child flow.
* **Rules:** Never show full answer; wording adapts to attempt history; optional 10–15 s cooldown before next hint (with soft countdown or message).

