## 12B. GLOBAL PAGES & STATES

### 404 / Not Found
* **Layout:** Centered; illustration (lost book or map); “This page wandered off!” — 24px; “Back to home” primary button; 16px subtext; child-friendly tone.

### Maintenance / Offline
* **Layout:** Full screen; “We’re making things even better”; “Back soon”; optional countdown or “Try again” button; 20px; no technical jargon.

### Cookie / Privacy Banner (Landing)
* **Position:** Bottom bar or floating bottom; max-width 480px on desktop; full width mobile.
* **Content:** Short text “We use cookies to save your progress and improve the app.”; “Accept” (primary) and “Learn more” (link to Privacy).
* **Dismiss:** Accept hides banner; “Learn more” opens policy in same tab or modal; no dark overlay for child.

### Legal Pages (Privacy, Terms, Contact)
* **Structure:** Title 24px; sections with H2 18px; body 16px; line-height 1.6; max-width 720px; back link “← Back to Readly”.
* **Contact:** Form — Name, Email, Message; 48px inputs; “Send” primary; success message inline.

