## 12C. EMPTY, LOADING & ERROR STATES

### Empty States (Pattern)
* **Layout:** Centered block; illustration (optional) 120–160px; title 18–20px; body 14–16px, `#718096`; single primary CTA; padding 32px.
* **Child:** Friendly illustration; “No stories yet” / “More coming soon!” — never “You have no data.”

### Loading States
* **Page load:** Full-page or in-content spinner — soft primary color; 40px; or skeleton blocks matching content (cards, lines).
* **Button:** Inline spinner 20px; label “Saving…” / “Loading…”; button disabled.
* **List/grid:** Skeleton cards (gray blocks, radius 12px); 4–6 placeholders; no shimmer if reduce-motion.

### Skeleton Specs
* **Card:** Rectangle 160px height; radius 16px; subtle gray bg `#E2E8F0`.
* **Line:** Height 16px; radius 4px; 80% width; same gray.
* **Avatar:** Circle 40px; same gray.

### Error States
* **Inline (form):** Red border 2px; message below field; bg `#FEE2E2`, text `#B91C1C`, 14px; icon optional.
* **Network / session:** Full message “Something went wrong. Check your connection and try again.”; “Try again” button; 18px; no stack trace for child.
* **Session expired:** “Your session ended. Please log in again.”; “Log in” CTA; redirect to auth.

### Toasts / Notifications
* **Position:** Bottom-center (mobile) or top-right (desktop); max-width 360px; z-index 300.
* **Content:** Icon (success / info / gentle error) 24px; message 14px; auto-dismiss 4–5 s or “Dismiss”.
* **Style:** Card surface; shadow modal; radius 12px; success = green tint, error = soft red tint.
* **Child:** “Progress saved!” / “Great job!” — no technical errors in toast.

