## 12D. COMPONENT LIBRARY (STATES & VARIANTS)

### Buttons
| Variant | Bg | Border | Text | Use |
|---------|-----|--------|------|-----|
| Primary | `#5B8DEF` | none | white | CTAs |
| Secondary | transparent | 2px `#5B8DEF` | `#5B8DEF` | Secondary actions |
| Ghost | transparent | none | `#2D3748` | Tertiary, “Cancel” |
| Danger | `#E8A5A5` or soft red | none | dark | Admin: delete (never child-facing) |
* **States:** Hover (darken 5–8%); Active (press 2px inset or scale 0.98); Disabled (opacity 0.5, no pointer); Loading (spinner + disabled).
* **Sizes:** Small 36px height, 14px; Default 48px, 16px; Large 56px, 18px.

### Inputs
* **Default:** 48px height; 16px font; border 2px `#E2E8F0`; radius 12px; focus ring 2px primary.
* **States:** Error — border `#E8A5A5`, message below; Disabled — bg `#F7FAFC`, cursor not-allowed.
* **Helper text:** 14px, `#718096`, 8px above or below; **Placeholder:** 16px min (iOS zoom).

### Modals
* **Overlay:** `rgba(0,0,0,0.4)`; click to close optional (prefer explicit “Close” for child).
* **Content:** Max-width 480px (child) or 560px (admin); padding 24–32px; radius 20px; shadow modal.
* **Header:** Title 20px; close icon top-right 40px touch target.
* **Footer:** Actions right-aligned; primary + secondary; 16px gap.
* **Focus trap:** Tab cycles inside modal; Escape closes.

### Dropdowns / Selects
* **Trigger:** Same height as inputs; chevron right; 16px label.
* **Panel:** Below trigger; shadow card; max-height 280px; scroll; option 48px height (touch); hover bg `#F8FAFC`.
* **Child:** Prefer chips or large option cards over small native select.

### Tooltips
* **Trigger:** Icon or text; 40px target.
* **Content:** 12–14px; max-width 200px; bg `#2D3748`, text white; padding 8px 12px; radius 8px; arrow 8px.
* **Position:** Prefer above to avoid overlap with nav; show on hover (desktop) or long-press (mobile optional).

### Pagination
* **Admin only:** “Previous” / “Next” + “Page 1 of 5”; or numbered 1 2 3 …; 40px targets; current page primary bg.

